#galleryContent.flexRow
  .fixedWidth.flexColumn
    #studyPane.pane
      p This will contain the overview histogram, summarizing each study
    #studyTextPane.pane
      p This pane will contain rendered markdown, describing a selected study in detail
  .growing.flexColumn
    #pagingPane.pane
      #seekFirst.button
      #seekPrev.button
      #pageSizeControl
        label(for='#pageSize') Page Size:
        input#pageSize(type='number',value='50')
      #seekNext.button
      #seekLast.button
      .spacer
      #toggleHistogram.button
    .growing.flexRow
      #imageWall.pane.growing
      #histogramPane.fixedWidth.pane
        p This will contain histograms, allowing users to filter images by metadata.
          These are the possible histograms that will be layered within each other:
        ol
          li Overview histograms, describing the entire dataset
          li Study histograms, describing the selected study
          li Filter histograms, describing the current filtered set of images
          li Page histograms, describing the currently visible images
      #imageDetailsPane.fixedWidth.pane
        p This pane will show details about a selected image
